com.pb.aquavis.emfac2011

Class Emfac2011Runner

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.aquavis.emfac2011.Emfac2011Runner
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TahoeEmfac2011Runner

    public class Emfac2011Runner
extends java.lang.Object
    The Emfac2011Runner class is used to generate an EMFAC2011 SG input file adjusted for travel demand model results, and then run (via the end user) the EMFAC2011 SG model using those inputs.

    • Method Detail

      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String... args)

      • runEmfac2011

        public void runEmfac2011(Emfac2011Data emfac2011Data)
        Run the EMFAC2011 model. This method will process the model results (via AquaVis outputs), create an adjusted EMFAC2011 input file, and initiate the EMFAC2011 SG model. Because of the way it is set up, the user must actually set up and run the EMFAC2011 SG model, but this method will create a dialog window which will walk the user through the steps required to do that.
        Parameters:
        emfac2011Data - The Emfac2011Data instance corresponding to the model results/run.
